    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving unit utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a cross-bank exhaust manifold to produce a visceral 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers crisp, rev-matched downshifts, while the Variable M Differential Lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This example features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable compression and rebound cycles. Recent service includes a preventive throttle actuator replacement and a fresh 10W-60 synthetic oil service. While showing minor signs of use typical for its age, the powertrain remains tight and the subframe bushings are in excellent order. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car ready for immediate spirited use.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
