      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips one would expect from careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably preserved; the premium upholstery is free of rips or stains, the carpets have been protected by floor mats, and every button and switch performs its function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The engine idles quietly and pulls strongly through the gears, while the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. With a fresh oil change, newer tires, and a detailed service history included, this car is ready for the open road. It is a clean, honest example that looks and drives beautifully.",
      "price": 36500.0,
